      },
      "date": "2011-04-22 11:54:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nComments about patch. The request dropping is not enough in ptlrpc_check_req() because these replays are still kept in client queue and will be replayed upon next recovery.\nI added class_export_fail() for exports which has replays in wrong phase, so client will be evicted and reconnect.\nThe error code is ENODEV because replay_interpret will do immediate reconnect in that case.",
